channel.title: AspectX - Custom Maps - Stable - Much more
channel.description:
Hi, I decided to release my Source and Client because am going to start a new server and rewrite almost all. But here anyway. I added some custom maps with simple RS2 Map editor and it works realy well. Over 200 Objects added. Turmoil added And some bugs Fixed. It is pretty Good and Idc if you leech this or not...
Base: OverloadX
Features: Custom Unique Home Dclaws Spec Working Pker,Mod and admin Cape Great Jframe Much More...
Download(d): Source and client (Package): [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?38hihc8iebkb880]Final Project.rar[/url]
Media: [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/mbmnb9.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/qywtba.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://img571.imageshack.us/img571/1757/30363536.th.png[/img] [IMG]http://img715.imageshack.us/img715/1936/99738896.th.png[/img]
I dont care what you think. Its just for people who want it to Learn some Programming and it is not my best work so dont flame me...
